---
// @ts-nocheck
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro'
import TopLayout from '@layouts/TopLayout.astro'
import BottomLayout from '@layouts/BottomLayout.astro'

const title = 'Getting Started'
---

<PageLayout
  title={title}
  description="Jump into the world of AGI OS - it's easier than you think!">
  <TopLayout>
    <div class="animate">
      <div
        class="page-heading text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-6">
        {title}
      </div>
    </div>
  </TopLayout>
  <BottomLayout>
    <article class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto px-4 animate">
      <p>Ready to explore the power of AI? AGI OS is as easy as 1, 2, 3!</p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
        1. Download AgentFlow (Your AI Playground)
      </h3>
      <p>
        AgentFlow is the visual interface where you build and interact with your
        AI. Think of it like a digital drawing board for your AI ideas! It runs
        right in your web browser – no complicated setup required.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <b>Privacy-focused:</b> Your data stays safe on your computer – no need
          to share anything online.
        </li>
        <li><b>Easy Install:</b> Download and run – it's ready in minutes!</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="text-center my-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/andraz/AgentFlow"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-primary">
          Download AgentFlow
        </a>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
        2. (Optional) Get Agent.js for Advanced AI
      </h3>
      <p>
        Want to use powerful language AI models? Agent.js acts as a bridge,
        connecting AgentFlow to those AI capabilities. Don't worry, it's
        designed for privacy too!
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <b>Keeps things secure:</b> Your AI keys and data stay safe on your computer.
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Works offline:</b> Use AI even without an internet connection (great
          for experimenting!).
        </li>
        <li>
          <b>Completely optional:</b> You only need it if you want to use advanced
          AI features.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="text-center my-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/andraz/Agent.js"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-primary">
          Download Agent.js (Optional)
        </a>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Start Building Your AI!</h3>
      <p>
        You're all set! Dive into the world of AGI OS and see what amazing
        things you can create.
      </p>
    </article>
  </BottomLayout>
</PageLayout>
